      <h2>Choosing your size</h2>
      <p>Our clothes are slim fitting and are designed for athletes. We’ve worked on the basis that your physical proportions are within a normal range for high-level adventure sport, and that you’re below 20% body fat. If you are outside of this range our clothes are unlikely to fit you well. We are not a fashion brand.</p>
      <p>The best way to determine your size is to click on S, M, L, XL below for more detailed arm, neck and chest measurements for each product and size.</p>
      <p>From our testing, chest measurement is key in the fit of these two products. Athletes with wider and deeper chests, like big wave surfers and mountaineers, should look at the measurements for their normal size plus the size up. Athletes with narrower slimmer chests, like ultra runners and climbers, should look at the measurements for their normal size plus the size down.</p>
